ifOutDscPct	: red		: 5	: {ifDescr}{ifAliasBox} - High output discard rate ({ifOutDscPct}%)

ifInDps         : yellow        : 1     : {ifDescr}{ifAliasBox} - Low input discard rate. ({ifInDps})
